  <brief_title>Reproducibility and Comparison of Platelet Function Assays With Aspirin and Clopidogrel (MK-0000-167)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Cross-over Study Using Aspirin and Clopidogrel to Assess Reproducibility and Compare Platelet Function Assays</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
