  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate whether the antiplatelet effects of Aspirin 300 mg daily and
      Clopidogrel 75 mg daily can be reproducibly measured using several point of care platelet
      function assays
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
